comments: Vucevic (CHI) extends his left arm into the back of Gallinari (ATL) during the rebound and the contact displaces Gallinari from his legal position.
Huerter (ATL) briefly touches the left arm of LaVine (CHI) at the start of the latter's drive but the marginal contact has no impact on LaVine's SQBR.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the out-of-bounds call on the floor pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Dosunmu (CHI) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and the Hawks are given possession.
Huerter (ATL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Dosunmu (CHI) and incidental contact occurs during the screen.

Green (CHI) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and partially dislodges it from Gallinari (ATL). Dosunmu (CHI) then comes in and makes contact with the ball that fully dislodges it but Gallinari is then able to recover the ball.

LaVine (CHI) has his left foot extended in the path of Young's (ATL) drive and Young steps forward with his right foot onto LaVine's foot. The foot to foot contact causes Young to slip and fall during the drive.
Bogdanovic (ATL) does not move into the landing area of DeRozan (CHI) and the marginal foot to foot contact occurs during DeRozan's slight extension of his right foot.
Dosunmu (CHI) moves alongside of Young's (ATL) path to the basket and marginal contact occurs as Young attempts his driving shot attempt.
Young (ATL) grasps the jersey of Dosunmu (CHI) during the driving shot attempt but the brief marginal hold does not impact Dosunmu's legal contest.

Bogdanovic (ATL) steps in during the turnaround shot attempt and marginal lower leg contact occurs between him and DeRozan (CHI) as DeRozan extends his leg during his shooting motion. The contact does not impact DeRozan's shot attempt.
Green (CHI) and Gallinari (ATL) jostle for positioning in the post. Green attempts to front the post and lower body contact occurs that does not rise to the level of a foul.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of LaVine (CHI) and absorbs the incidental contact during the pick.
Vucevic (CHI) legally contests the shot attempt by Bogdanovic (ATL).
Gallinari (ATL) commits a take foul on Green (CHI).
LaVine (CHI) legally contests the shot attempt by Gallinari (ATL).
